<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>ASP.NET SignalR 2.x</h1>
    <p class="lead">Demos for SignalR 2.0 and upcoming 2.x releases.</p>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/DamianEdwards/SignalR-2.x-demo" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get the code &raquo;</a></p>
